  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique was forbidden and sealed due to its utterly inhumane effects, which are meant to shut down all the target's senses over time. The subject is @Condition[blind]{blinded} and deafened. It loses all sense of taste and texture, cannot smell, and loses its sense of touch (including its sense of pain), so it can't tell if it's standing, sitting, falling, whether it has been damaged, etc. The subject is unable to sense Chakra, and must make a Will save each round to avoid becoming unable to act.<br><br>Even though the subject is @Condition[blind]{blinded}, it is still subject to gaze attacks (since the blindness is merely an illusion). The subject further suffers a -4 penalty to Massive Damage saves.<br><br>This technique can be dispelled, but counts as a Rank 12 technique for those attempting to do so.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
